reviewText: We bought the SM Town in NY at Madison Square Gardens and absolutely LOVED it.  So when this came up, we had to buy it, but were disappointed that it was severely edited and didn't get to see all the performances of the groups and it was not of the same quality as the one from NY.  Plus, this was more expensive than the other one and I expected more.  I am still glad I got it, as I got to have Shinee performing Sherlock on it and also the performance by f(x) which they performed more than 1 song, but we only got to see 1.
